<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" itunes:timing="Line" xml:lang="en"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/></metadata></head><body dur="02:57.934"><div begin="00:32.849" end="02:57.934"><p begin="00:32.849" end="00:40.665" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1">We ignore refused consent</p><p begin="00:40.665" end="00:48.678" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2">Animals do not repent</p><p begin="00:48.678" end="00:56.674" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3">Courtesy to intervene</p><p begin="00:56.674" end="01:03.256" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4">Weathered down my selfish needs</p><p begin="01:03.256" end="01:05.439" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5">I suffocate</p><p begin="01:05.439" end="01:13.670" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6">And promise me you won't resuscitate</p><p begin="01:13.670" end="01:20.365" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7">And if I change my mind it's far too late</p><p begin="01:20.365" end="01:27.806" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8">I'm wasting my days as I've wasted my nights and I've wasted my youth</p><p begin="01:27.806" end="01:31.694" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9">You're waiting for something</p><p begin="01:31.694" end="01:36.865" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10">You've waited in vain because there's nothing for you</p><p begin="01:36.865" end="01:37.751" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11">Suffocation</p><p begin="01:53.007" end="02:00.746" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12">Humility yet to be seen</p><p begin="02:00.746" end="02:08.660" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13">Models made of plasticine</p><p begin="02:08.660" end="02:16.839" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14">Morality disgrace us now</p><p begin="02:16.839" end="02:23.368" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15">Entertain and take a bow</p><p begin="02:23.368" end="02:25.578" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16">I suffocate</p><p begin="02:25.578" end="02:33.634" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17">And promise me you won't resuscitate</p><p begin="02:33.634" end="02:39.733" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18">And if I change my mind it's far too late</p><p begin="02:39.733" end="02:47.373" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19">I'm wasting my days as I've wasted my nights and I've wasted my youth</p><p begin="02:47.373" end="02:51.778" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20">You're waiting for something</p><p begin="02:51.778" end="02:57.018" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21">You've waited in vain because there's nothing for you</p><p begin="02:57.018" end="02:57.934" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22">Suffocation</p></div></body></tt>